20:54.519 --> 20:56.543
Baby's at the ready...

20:57.518 --> 20:58.652
Oh, yeah.

20:58.687 --> 21:00.654
In three, two,

21:00.688 --> 21:01.622
one, roll!

21:01.656 --> 21:02.689
Come on, Emma, come here!

21:02.724 --> 21:04.491
- Roll!
- Come on, Emma. Roll to daddy.

21:04.525 --> 21:06.493
- Roll roll roll.
- Dan: This way, lead with your head.

21:06.527 --> 21:08.661
( All chattering )

21:09.696 --> 21:11.531
All: Oh!

21:11.565 --> 21:13.465
Are you kidding? Emma.

21:13.500 --> 21:14.565
Oh.

21:14.599 --> 21:16.664
- Double or nothing?
- You're on.

21:16.698 --> 21:19.298
- ( Laughing )
- Gentlemen, place your bets.

21:19.333 --> 21:20.700
<i>It's time for baby roll.</i>

